title: Banana prune muffins
ingredients: ['100g caster sugar', '4 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1 egg', '225g mashed banana', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '200g plain flour', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '175g chopped pitted prunes']
